title: msg()
brief: Write a message to the status-area.
----

<p>The bottom row of the <tt>lumail</tt> mail-client is designated as the message area.</p>
<p>The <tt>msg</tt> function may be used to write a line of text to this area.</p>
<p>Example:</p>
<pre>
msg( "I am alive!" );
msg( "Today is " .. os.date() );
</pre>